{"tid":2463970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"用黃藍做唯一界線去界定本土文化係錯誤既思考方法","createTime":"2021-03-27T06:18:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T08:47:15.000Z","uid":61886,"like":29,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6fc113da638e1df3e88e77f1f4f73f7b14a39368","tid":2463970,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T06:18:18.000Z","msg":"大家所講 革命唔係一朝一日所達成<br />\n喺現階段運動低迷既時期<br />\n保育香港本土文化係其中一個需要大家去做既事<br />\n(手足被捕/獄中/獄後支援都好重要)<br />\n<br />\n香港人=香港文化精神組成<br />\n香港文化=語言+藝術+運動+生活<br />\n<br />\n語言：廣東話 (中共提行普通話授課)<br />\n藝術：電影、音樂 (中共用無限金錢將香港藝人拉去奶共，扼殺本土創作）<br />\n運動：香港代表隊 (中共刻意製造運動搵唔到錢，令香港人放棄運動，但運動係凝聚身份好重要既方式）<br />\n<br />\n中共製造嘅文化侵略 （抖音 匪語）<br />\n就係軟性消滅香港文化<br />\n<br />\n當你只識用黃藍去界定<br />\n就會誤判左好多本土既文化<br />\n<br />\n我立場好簡單<br />\n對香港本土文化有幫助既我都支持<br />\n無論係本土音樂 電影 定體育<br />\n有助建構香港人既本土文化<br />\n建立香港人身份既都係值得支持<br />\n<br />\n一秒拳王、試當真、香港足球隊、viutv<br />\n都係我會支持既<br />\n<br />\n利申<br />\n歡迎討論，罵戰既不會回應"},{"pid":"8b31497def7c861361a89dfe74668b92b7041960","tid":2463970,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T06:18:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61104d5fe6c63ffcda7a807be41529c09546d4ed","tid":2463970,"uid":307981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T06:19:24.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"a8431c4bd0b17944fbf60da14731965f2ab40ce5","tid":2463970,"uid":262834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T06:21:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea493ab4334782188301ea25b63ef19567f50cb4","tid":2463970,"uid":205043,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T06:22:26.000Z","msg":"cctoy用黃藍做界定，根本就係畫地自限<br />\n<br />\n都未講佢地對黃既標準扯到幾高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec71985010426fe6ce3a91e931ca2ebc5f2546f","tid":2463970,"uid":351302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T06:23:20.000Z","msg":"除咗電影同音樂外<br />\n希望大家多啲留意本地文學 舞台劇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過希望同時唔好將文化藝術政治化<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d962d7e983c2758a12e233f85e5ab2c98c1dc3","tid":2463970,"uid":303604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T06:23:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e385780568f150ccf4e2d58caedc983c32a0c1a","tid":2463970,"uid":24737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T06:24:36.000Z","msg":"lm睇大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f46ea7f4d4aa37296bb13f7e7bbcd3fe36bb35e","tid":2463970,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ea493ab4334782188301ea25b63ef19567f50cb4","tid":2463970,"uid":205043,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T06:22:26.000Z","msg":"cctoy用黃藍做界定，根本就係畫地自限<br />\n<br />\n都未講佢地對黃既標準扯到幾高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T06:26:44.000Z","msg":"所以我已經好少喺時事台出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcaf9f09bd4f61d1685bca5a1a25379aa028a60d","tid":2463970,"uid":228995,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ea493ab4334782188301ea25b63ef19567f50cb4","tid":2463970,"uid":205043,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T06:22:26.000Z","msg":"cctoy用黃藍做界定，根本就係畫地自限<br />\n<br />\n都未講佢地對黃既標準扯到幾高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T06:55:52.000Z","msg":"鬥<br />\n<br />\n近日香港人喜歡鬥黃。「鬥」這個字可以解比較，亦可以解批鬥的鬥，很多時由比較發展到批鬥。依我們看來：「爭咩吖，溝埋做瀨尿牛丸吖笨。」<br />\n<br />\n比較<br />\n<br />\n其實比較是好事，有比較才有進步。但我們要想想為甚麼要比較。假如我們比較過後，發覺接受不了別人不夠黃，那一開始我們說甚麼「兄弟爬山，各自努力」？我們不是接受了人人崗位不同，可以各有付出？黃色也可以有很多種的。<br />\n<br />\n況且就當你真的較黃，那又如何？有獎品？如果真黃的門檻如此高，變相就會排斥很多不夠黃、淺黃的人。我不知道確定了超黃的意義，但我只知道多一個淺黃總比鬥走一個淺黃好。慢慢下去，你就會發現站你那邊的人愈來愈少。<br />\n<br />\n批鬥<br />\n<br />\n談到批鬥的老祖宗，當然數老共。雖然人家的批鬥由上而下，無論規模、程度都遠超我們，但亦有一點點類似的地方。他們批鬥的，也是不夠左、不夠堅定支持革命的人。<br />\n<br />\n以往看史書我們懂得說荒謬、也懂得說要以史為鑒，但偏偏到發生在自己身上就不明白這顯淺道理。如果不夠左不是錯，那不夠黃也不是錯。<br />\n<br />\n我們不應訂立一個理想然後要人人都做得到，否則就是死罪。有理想很好，我們可以向理想進發，但未夠理想不等於錯。不要因為別人不夠黃而批鬥，應該因為別人有點黃而高興。因為黃從來不是絕對指標，而是程度，多一點點就是多了，也是好了。勿以善少而不為。善少也是善。<br />\n<br />\n況且假如就算真的要夠黃，但若然我們都當淺黃的對方是命運共同體的手足，而不是文革時期那些反革命的敵人，那我們不應看待彼此的關係為你死我活的對立關係，反應考慮黃圈不只是一個圈，更是一個同喜同悲的群體，自己友有問題咪勸囉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/鬥黃/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%AC%A5%E9%BB%83%2F&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWooeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=9fe0cdd0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%AC%A5%E9%BB%83%2F&h=5555cea5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/鬥黃/</a>"},{"pid":"eb179c035fa1b97eeeb61d392f527b6c36f0b13c","tid":2463970,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T06:57:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f0dbc8f5e20b28963860294df46482a42aec12","tid":2463970,"uid":84783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T06:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce3d8cdf7a133a25a2936e043307f3facefc9ba2","tid":2463970,"uid":319935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ea493ab4334782188301ea25b63ef19567f50cb4","tid":2463970,"uid":205043,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T06:22:26.000Z","msg":"cctoy用黃藍做界定，根本就係畫地自限<br />\n<br />\n都未講佢地對黃既標準扯到幾高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T07:00:14.000Z","msg":"用cctoy 非cctoy做界定，根本就係畫地自限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申:唔反對你所講嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"753b683f5b9fe5df8331808954ec949b9c4f28d3","tid":2463970,"uid":312430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T07:06:15.000Z","msg":"黃藍誰來定錯對<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自從cctoy搞鳩達哥開始就已經對佢哋口中嘅黃絲好失望"},{"pid":"b861828e4d8daeaa911351bea2f35c71f5d2ed50","tid":2463970,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T07:14:37.000Z","msg":"好似環保咁<br />\n<br />\n喺能力範圍內選擇相近嘅替代品<br />\n不必要嘅就唔睇唔用唔幫襯<br />\n避唔到嘅儘量少用<br />\n<br />\n鼓吹/鼓勵代替苛責"},{"pid":"349fd77628e9757ffb7258b19ed988c439f6bf43","tid":2463970,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"753b683f5b9fe5df8331808954ec949b9c4f28d3","tid":2463970,"uid":312430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T07:06:15.000Z","msg":"黃藍誰來定錯對<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自從cctoy搞鳩達哥開始就已經對佢哋口中嘅黃絲好失望"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T08:21:39.000Z","msg":"用黃藍黎做任何事既界線<br />\n只係因為自己缺乏思考能力"},{"pid":"2357a74c491eb78c8877ee55523ec5dd88b3c0ca","tid":2463970,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T08:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}